Big Brother Naija reality star, Nengi has revealed why she was not friends with Erica in the house. Nengi during her media rounds said she was not friends with Erica because she does not know how to force friendships. Erica had broken down in tears because people she knew outside the house were not her friends in the reality show. She had also approached Nengi to discuss the situation but they still were not friends However, when asked why they were not friends despite being ex-beauty queens, she said, ”You know how social media is, you might know someone, follow each other but you have not had conversations with them. ”In the entertainment industry you meet people, follow them on social media but that does not mean we are friends. I don’t know how to force friendships.”